title: Why its Never Been a Better Time to be a Creator
description: People often say they would love to be a creator, but feel it's too late to make the jump. Reed and Blake break down why it's actually never been a more perfect time to start your creator journey. With so many platforms, tools, and resources to choose from, we hope this video encourages those to take the leap and see how they can grow as a creator themselves.
